headline: Assessing Welltower After a 53% Surge and Lofty Earnings Multiple in 2025
summary: If you have been wondering whether Welltower is still worth buying after its big run, you are not alone. That is exactly the question this breakdown aims to tackle. The stock has cooled slightly with a 5.4% dip over the last week and a flat 30-day return, but it is still up 53.2% year to date, 51.2% over 1 year, and more than tripled over 3 and 5 years. Behind those gains, investors have been reacting to Welltower's expanding senior housing footprint, new partnerships with leading operators,...
